# Pages and templates

Required frontmatter for new pages under `src/pages/`:

```yaml
title: Page Title
date: "ISO-8601"
template: regular-static-page  # must match src/templates/<template>.tsx
```

After adding a page, add its `title` to `src/settings/nav-menu.md` `ordering` if it should appear in the nav.

Templates use GraphQL `pageQuery` with `$id: String!` and wrap content in `Layout` + `Seo`. Copy an existing template before inventing new patterns.

`releases-page` loads CHANGELOG from GitHub at runtime—do not duplicate release notes in markdown unless asked.
